<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٥ -<span style="color:#707070">[مِنْهَا قَوْلهم]</span> : <span style="color:#950000">" خَادِمُ الْفُقَرَاءِ يُحْشَرُ مَعَ الأَنْبِيَاءِ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٦ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" عَلَيْكُمْ بِدِينِ الْعَجَائِزِ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٧ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" الْفَقْرُ فَخْرِي "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٨ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلهم:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" لولاك <span style="color:#707070">[لَوْلاكَ]</span> لَمَا خَلَقْتُ الأَفْلاكَ "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>